data.description: Cute 2 bed 1 bath home on a large corner lot. The large back yard has a detached garage with a bit of extra spaced added on. This home has  unique rod iron fence in the front and privacy fence in the back. The large kitchen has lots of space and a rod iron pot hanger for added appeal. The wood and laminate floors can be beautiful again with a bit of love. This home as a lot of charm and could be brought back to life. Home is "sold as is" and would be a great investment home but could be a great starter home.
